node.text: Good Afternoon!!✨🌞It’s been a busy weekend packing orders and working on new decor!!🌸 So far I’ve packed over 150 orders and I still have about 120 left. Then I’ll be moving on to the pre orders!!💕 I can’t thank you all enough for your patience and support !! And as always if you have any questions about your order feel free to message me via dm anytime. Have a blessed day everyone !!✨💕🤗

node.text: So in love with this Crystal Moon Sun Catcher Collection!!☀️🔮Featuring my signature amethyst crystal moon mirror and amethyst moon slices!! These beauties sold during my last restock but I cannot wait to make more!!✨It’s been a busy couple weeks wrapping sun catchers and working on pre orders!!! I can’t thank you all enough for your patience and support!! Orders will begin shipping out today, tracking numbers will be sent via email💕 Have a blessed day everyone!!🌿(if you have any questions about your order feel free to send me a dm)

My little helper King!💕 He loves to be in the middle of everything.✨🌸I’ll be spending the day shipping out orders and organizing new stock!! Can’t wait to show everyone the new aura colors I’ve been working on.💕Thank you all again for your love and endless support!!💕PS. I’ve been getting an alarming amount of dm’s and comments stating my items are arriving broken. Only to find out these items were purchased with scam shops using my content, claiming to sell my handmade work. (The only place my items are sold is through my website sacraluna)😵 I will continue to post about this issue since there are new scam sites popping up everyday. A huge thank you to everyone for sending me dms and screenshots to help me get these pages taken down. 💕

node.text:
Good Afternoon!!✨🌞It’s been a busy week wrapping up sun catchers and prepping goodie bags for everyone’s orders!!💕Each order will include one tea light candle, 4 soft touch picture cards, 3 incense cones (if you ordered a cauldron or incense holder) and a bag stuffed with extra crystals! The crystal bags will include a variety of amethyst, rose quartz, grey moonstone, carnelian, peach aventurine, blue tigers eye, garnet, clear quartz and white howlite!✨💕Thank you all so much for your love and support!! 
PS! If you sent an email regarding address updates, shipping or cancelation. Please check your spam folder. I sent out over 40 emails last week and want to make sure they reach everyone!! Have a blessed day!!🌸🌞

node.text: Good Afternoon !!✨I just want to give a huge thank you to everyone who checked out my restock on Friday!!🌸😭💕 I can’t believe everything sold out in less then 20 minutes!! Words cannot express how grateful I am for all your love and support!! Sacra Luna is solely run by myself and I do everything from designs to creating, videos, photography, shipping, tik tok, IG, dms , emails , comments. At times it can be a little overwhelming so I want to thank all the supportive comments and dms I have received!! So excited to show everyone all the new designs and crystals I’ve been working on!! node.text: ✨A huge THANK YOU to everyone for all the support you’ve shown me these last two weeks!✨💕My new decor received such an amazing response and unfortunately there’s been an alarming amount of scam ads popping up on Facebook, Instagram and Etsy using my content! They’re also using my descriptions to trick buyers into thinking they’re an extension of my shop. My handmade decor is only available through my site sacraluna(link in bio). My Instagram is Sacraluna and my tiktok is Sacralunajewelry. If you see these ads using my videos, please do not buy! Report, Tag me or send me screenshots so I can report the post directly. So far I’ve removed over 58 ads and I’m trying my best to help those who purchased from these sites get a refund. The sites will usually have a huge discount for the item like $28.99! but not have any detailed photos. Just screenshots from my page. This became a huge issue for me on TikTok since many were questioning if I was even the real creator. Luckily my Instagram showcases my work for the last 9 years and documents the progress of my journey as an artist. I’ve posted videos of my apartment countless times in my stories. My cats, my tattoos and my studio. This battle of taking down scammers has been going on for about 5 months but luckily I have the best support system and I cannot be more grateful for all of you!!!😭💕💕Thank you all so much for defending me, sharing my work in your stories, posting me on your page, just chatting with me when you know I’m feeling overwhelmed. I am blessed to have you all in my life 😭💕
